    <li>Outdoor Safety: If you're outside, seek shelter immediately. Avoid tall objects such as trees or open fields, and never take shelter under isolated trees.</li>
   
    <li>Unplug Electronics: To prevent damage from power surges caused by lightning strikes, unplug electronic devices and appliances.</li>
    <li>Emergency Kit: Have an emergency kit ready with essentials such as water, non-perishable food, a flashlight, batteries, a first aid kit, and any necessary medications.</li>
  
    </ul>`;
    
